{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Lou6iaykHjWxYZz86gQiVx","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I've found the exact response shapes for all three endpoints. Here's the detailed breakdown:\n\n---\n\n## 1. GET /me (from profile.ts, line 35-96)\n\n**Success Response (200):**\n```json\n{\n  \"userId\": string,\n  \"username\": string,\n  \"avatarUrl\": string | null,\n  \"heatMultiplier\": number,\n  \"pointsBalance\": string,\n  \"stats\": {\n    \"gamesPlayed\": number,\n    \"totalWagered\": string,\n    \"totalWins\": number,\n    \"winRate\": number,\n    \"winStreakCurrent\": number,\n    \"winStreakBest\": number,\n    \"netPnl\": string,\n    \"gameBreakdown\": {\n      [gameName: string]: {\n        \"gamesPlayed\": number,\n        \"totalWagered\": string,\n        \"totalWins\": number,\n        \"winRate\": number,\n        \"netPnl\": string\n      }\n    }\n  },\n  \"usernameNextEditAt\": string | null,\n  \"createdAt\": string\n}\n```\n\n**Error Responses:**\n- 401: `{ \"error\": \"Authentication required\" }`\n- 404: `{ \"error\": \"PROFILE_NOT_FOUND\" }`\n- 500: `{ \"error\": \"Failed to fetch profile\" }`\n\n---\n\n## 2. PUT /username (from profile.ts, line 99-163)\n\n**Success Response (200):**\n```json\n{\n  \"username\": string,\n  \"nextEditAvailableAt\": string | null\n}\n```\n\n**Error Responses:**\n- 400: `{ \"error\": \"INVALID_FORMAT\" }`\n- 401: `{ \"error\": \"Authentication required\" }`\n- 404: `{ \"error\": \"PROFILE_NOT_FOUND\" }`\n- 409: `{ \"error\": \"USERNAME_TAKEN\" }`\n- 429: `{ \"error\": \"COOLDOWN_ACTIVE\", \"nextEditAvailableAt\": string }`\n- 500: `{ \"error\": \"Failed to update username\" }`\n\n---\n\n## 3. GET /:identifier (from public-profile.ts, line 18-48)\n\n**Success Response (200):**\n```json\n{\n  \"userId\": string,\n  \"username\": string,\n  \"avatarUrl\": string | null,\n  \"heatMultiplier\": number,\n  \"stats\": {\n    \"gamesPlayed\": number,\n    \"totalWins\": number,\n    \"winRate\": number\n  },\n  \"createdAt\": string\n}\n```\n\n**Error Responses:**\n- 404: `{ \"error\": \"NOT_FOUND\" }`\n- 500: `{ \"error\": \"Failed to fetch profile\" }`\n\n---\n\n**Key Differences:**\n- **GET /me** includes `pointsBalance`, full `stats` with `totalWagered`, `netPnl`, streaks, and `gameBreakdown`; also includes `usernameNextEditAt`\n- **GET /:identifier** (public) is a stripped-down version with only `gamesPlayed`, `totalWins`, and `winRate` in stats—no `pointsBalance`, no breakdown, no wagering/PnL data"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e44550f8-11fe-49dd-bb57-a4d026a1433a","uuid":"9fc0738e-d1f9-491c-96fc-ee8a15325fac","timestamp":"2026-03-31T15:20:37.597Z","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Read these two files and report back the exact response shapes (the JSON objects returned in c.json() calls) for each endpoint:\n\n1. /workspaces/rng-utopia/backend/services/backend/src/routes/profile.ts - GET /me and PUT /username handlers\n2. /workspaces/rng-utopia/backend/services/backend/src/routes/public-profile.ts - GET /:identifier handler\n\nReport the exact field names, types, and nesting structure for each endpoint's response.","agentId":"a09c8f70c049c1b64","agentType":"Explore","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I've found the exact response shapes for all three endpoints. Here's the detailed breakdown:\n\n---\n\n## 1. GET /me (from profile.ts, line 35-96)\n\n**Success Response (200):**\n```json\n{\n  \"userId\": string,\n  \"username\": string,\n  \"avatarUrl\": string | null,\n  \"heatMultiplier\": number,\n  \"pointsBalance\": string,\n  \"stats\": {\n    \"gamesPlayed\": number,\n    \"totalWagered\": string,\n    \"totalWins\": number,\n    \"winRate\": number,\n    \"winStreakCurrent\": number,\n    \"winStreakBest\": number,\n    \"netPnl\": string,\n    \"gameBreakdown\": {\n      [gameName: string]: {\n        \"gamesPlayed\": number,\n        \"totalWagered\": string,